title: Ep. #140 | Catching Up: WOODZ
description:
WOODZ sits down to talk with Eric all about his latest EP "Only Lovers Left", days as a solo artist, and how he went from Korea to Brazil to the Philippines and then back to Korea to pursue his passion for music.

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
